## Size Config
#  Make scaling persist after death
scale persist set true
#  Change the delays to be fast
scale delay set pehkui:visibility 5
scale delay set pehkui:width 5
scale delay set pehkui:height 5
scale delay set pehkui:drops 5
scale delay set pehkui:hitbox_height 5
scale delay set pehkui:hitbox_width 5

## Set Size
scale set pehkui:visibility 0.7
scale set pehkui:width 0.7
scale set pehkui:height 0.7
scale set pehkui:drops 0.7

scale set pehkui:hitbox_height 0.95
scale set pehkui:hitbox_width 1